rComments: Dr. Webb was an amazing professor! He did a fantastic job leading our fourth year honours seminar on the geographies of youth in urban spaces. Would highly recommend taking one of his courses.

Professor Webb is an amazing teacher. When he lectures, he not only knows his material but is also really passionate about what he teaches which makes for a great time in his class. He's very caring and very accessible outside of class, he always responds to his emails. you need to attend his class to do well, but he makes class time interesting.
He's quite the incredible prof, always looked forward to his lectures

At the beginning of the sem his lectures were a little confusing and hard to follow as it was his first lecture, HOWEVER he improved so much by the end and was an amazing prof!!! always engaged with the class and when students gave answers/comments he always genuinely listened and respected their ideas. (Hes also beautiful) 10/10 would recommend
i love him IDSA01H3 was his first ever class he taught and he was amazing. i love him i love this man. great prof great person. i love this man.
really good prof! you can tell that he is passionate about his work. he even gives additional reading materials and documentaries in lecture if you are interested.
